03:39.952 --> 03:48.722
If your identity is then understood in and through the relationship that you have with Christ and you're a confident person, then you're not going to be comparing yourself to others.

03:48.994 --> 03:49.635
That's different.

03:49.935 --> 03:57.606
But if you're a prideful person, you put yourself up on a pedestal and then you try to lower everybody else around you because you need to feel good about yourself.

03:57.946 --> 03:59.969
You see, that's all coming from a place of insecurity.

04:00.329 --> 04:01.671
